flowchart LR
    User[Inventory user] --> UI[PySide6 desktop UI]
    UI --> VM[ViewModels\nMain / Preview / Label Item]
    VM --> ExcelSvc[ExcelService\nopenpyxl]
    VM --> PrintSvc[PrintService\nLabelRenderer + QPrinter]
    ExcelSvc --> Excel[(Inventory Excel\nHoja1)]
    PrintSvc --> Driver[Windows printer driver\nSATO WS408]
    Driver --> Printer[[SATO WS408\n48mm x 23mm labels]]
    UI --> Config[(App settings)]
    PrintSvc --> DriverCheck[DriverCheck\nQPrinterInfo]
    DriverCheck --> Driver
